and the winner is: 
	https://github.com/josegonzalez/python-github-backup

	warning: 
		https://github.com/josegonzalez/python-github-backup/issues/124

	usage:

pip install --user github-backup

github-backup  --releases --fork --private --gists --starred-gists --wikis --lfs --repositories --milestones --hooks --labels --pull-details --pull-commits  --pull-comments --pulls --issue-events  --issue-comments  --issues --all  --following --followers  --watched  --all-starred  --starred  --incremental  --repositories --private  --token XXXXXXXXXX --output-directory ./github_backup/0  koo5

# get a token here: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# for organizations, add --organization
# there is no way to make it get only open pull requests :|

